<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>
A plain <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> block (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.67</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.995</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">
0.535</measure>) probably a building <rs type="objectType">block</rs> rather than a statue base.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">
Inscribed</rs> on the face, within an area that has been smoothed; the whole stone apparently weathered.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Description of Letters</head>
<p><measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">
0.0175-0.0225</measure></p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="-0100" notAfter="0100" exact="none">First century B.C. to first century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
</div>

