<head>Text Constituted From</head>
<p>Preliminary transcription (Reynolds); Publications; Sherard papers; Deering; Gaudin.</p>
</div>

<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>Artemeis daughter of Poplios set up <supplied reason="subaudible" cert="low">a tomb for</supplied> Bacchios son of Poplios her brother in accordance with his will.</p>
</div>

